cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically with 3D and 2D human representations. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also involves human-computer interaction (HCI) and machine learning (ML) techniques, which suggest cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as likely categories. The use of 3D models and pose estimation techniques also suggests cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia) as possible categories.
